From 21f44f26b3afae92aee5814c6754f86fbbcd9927 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Olivier Benjamin <olivier.benjamin@bootlin.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Oct 2025 17:49:17 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] ELE: dirty fix includes

The headers in include/hsm/internal themselves include headers
in "internal", such as "internal/hsm_common_def.h"
This cannot work, and breaks for users of the library.
We cannot symlink, because we do not know the symroot's path here.

Signed-off-by: Olivier Benjamin <olivier.benjamin@bootlin.com>
